Package: FMIndexR
Title: FM Index Creation and Pattern Search
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gabriele", "Oliveto", email = "gabriele.oliveto@mail.polimi.it", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")))
Description: Generates all Data structures of FM index and looks for patterns 
    using Backward search. The provided FM index is composed of the suffix 
    array, the Burrows-Wheeler transform, the Occurrency matrix and the Count 
    array. The Backward search allows for fast pattern recognition and returns 
    the pattern indexes.
